OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe morning will start mostly
OL,6,Fcloudy with hill fog and patchy rain.
OL,7,FSkies brightening somewhat, with some
OL,8,Fwarm afternoon sunshine developing,
OL,9,Fespecially to the east of high ground.
OL,10,FStill a few showers though. Very mild,
OL,11,Fthough windy in the north.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FClear spells overnight,
OL,14,Fespecially in the east, with fog
OL,15,Fpatches. However, cloud thick enough
OL,16,Fto give patchy drizzle further west.
OL,17,FMore persistent rain arriving in the
OL,18,Fnorthwest, where remaining windy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
