OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FRain will move southeast
OL,6,Facross Scotland and Northern Ireland,
OL,7,Fwith brisk winds. Brighter in the
OL,8,Fnorthwest later. England and Wales
OL,9,Fmostly dry and cloudy, but occasional
OL,10,Fbright intervals and mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
